headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week on the Podium: Canis Seminole Frontier
content: Once you’ve gotten your fill of exhaust fumes for the evening, stop by the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort and give the Lucky Wheel a spin to walk away with GTA$, RP, snacks, clothing, and more. This week on the podium is the Canis Seminole Frontier, a sensible answer to the question: “How do we get these beers to the top of that mountain?”
